1. If performance is bad, blame it on your computer's specs, not the code
2. "There are no bugs. only unintended features." -Oogway
3. Marksmanship is bad, firepower is the only stat worth getting
4. If you get stuck, right click teleports you to the cursor.
5. If you lose, there is no way to restart. Get better at the game so you don't lose.